<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/814431-does-anyone-know-if-cat-turned-up-in-their">Does anyone know if Cat turned up in their other books? I loved that character and always wanted him to somehow have a happy ending.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_814431'><a id="like_count_community_question_814431" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/814431?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F679702.The_Windflower">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/814431-does-anyone-know-if-cat-turned-up-in-their">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/814431-does-anyone-know-if-cat-turned-up-in-their">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
