<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/41090467-angie"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1471616812i/41090467._UX100_CR0,51,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/41090467-angie">Angie</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">No, unfortunately Cat still waits for his own book! This character is a favorite for many readers (including myself!) and there is been a high demand <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">No, unfortunately Cat still waits for his own book! This character is a favorite for many readers (including myself!) and there is been a high demand for a sequel with him. The writers have mentioned in the past that they were interested in continuing his story but so far there aren't any news on a sequel. He isn't mentioned in any of their other novels. So, we just have to wait and see!<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
