        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/18402305-the-windflower">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15076466-maggieandteddy?shelf=i-want-it-on-kindle">i-want-it-on-kindle</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15076466-maggieandteddy?shelf=pirate-hero">pirate-hero</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15076466-maggieandteddy?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15076466-maggieandteddy?shelf=curious">curious</a>, 
